rows.label: tev036601_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev036601_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask May May about miranium.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev036601_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask May May about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask May May about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0001
rows.name:
During our voyage, I got my hands on many a
precious mineral, you see?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0002
rows.name:
But I have never worked with one as special as as
miranium, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0003
rows.name:
Depending on how you refine it, you can
make it harder than iron, or as squishy as
a sponge. It is incredible, don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0004
rows.name:
There might even be a way to derive energy from it
using fission?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0005
rows.name:
And this planet is littered with the miracle material!
Mira really is astounding, isn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0008
rows.name:
I'm working on a veritable super machine that can
convert miranium into a whole slew of materials,
you see?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0009
rows.name:
But once it is complete, we'll need more miranium
than ever, right? Literally oodles of of the stuff.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0010
rows.name:
So I need you to sell me as as much as you can find.
I filed a request with Mission Control—look for the
"Shimmer & Savvy Financial Group," if you would?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0025
rows.name: Welcome to the Shimmer & Savvy Financial Group![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0026
rows.name:
Are you ready for some big news? Because we have
finally completed our flagship alchemical device—
the Miranimogrifier![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0027
rows.name:
We'll buy your miranium at generous prices, okay?
Because what's the point of a Miranimogrifier with no
miranium to transmogrify?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0028
rows.name:
We're also planning to introduce a member rewards
program, so so check back often, all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask May May about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0029
rows.name:
A bronze member? Step right up, all right?
Business is booming![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0030
rows.name:
But I want to to make YOU happy, don't I?
Have you been selling your miranium?
We've increased our buyback rates![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0031
rows.name:
Anyway, check Mission Control for the details, okay?
Then cash that miranium in for big big credits![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0032
rows.name:
And even if the money doesn't matter, you don't want
to miss your chance to become a silver member, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask May May about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0033
rows.name:
Ah, a silver member? Step right up, please?
Thanks to you, our company's Miranimogrifier has
been alchemizing up a a storm.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0034
rows.name:
And right now, we're offering exceptional miranium
buyback rates exclusively to special partners like you,
all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0035
rows.name:
So gather up that miranium and lather up that wallet,
because this is your chance to shower yourself in
sweet sweet money, isn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_SEL3021
rows.name: Ask May May about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0036
rows.name:
Goodness me! Are you really a gold member?
Well then, welcome to Shimmer & Savvy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0037
rows.name:
You've made a rich Ma-non out of me, haven't you?
And now it's time for me to repay the favor.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0038
rows.name:
We're both going to be filthy rich, aren't we?
...Well, me first, but then you. Definitely then you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0039
rows.name:
I am going to give you some INCREDIBLE miranium
buyback rates, so check out Mission Control, okay?
Your wallet will be doing backflips of of joy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_SEL4011
rows.name: Ask May May about miranium.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_SEL4021
rows.name: Ask May May about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0040
rows.name: Well, I went to make a donation to BLADE, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0041
rows.name:
And along the way I met this charming researcher
named Kirsty. Do you know her? Anyway, we talked at
great length about the the wonders of miranium.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0042
rows.name:
Did you know that despite its value, the mineral can be
found in abundant supply all over the planet?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0043
rows.name:
It seems too good to be true—almost as if the planet
was designed by some mastermind to produce the
stuff?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0044
rows.name:
Kirsty said it was a gift from God, which...okay?
Guess I'd like to meet that guy if that's the case...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0045
rows.name:
He must be some insanely gifted technician to assemble
an entire planet, don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0048
rows.name:
A platinum member? Really? Holy wow!
...Hey, do you like grenade pizza?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0049
rows.name:
I practically live on the stuff these days, you know?
And what a life it it is...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0050
rows.name:
I don't even need money anymore, do I?
Also, I don't really give two pepperonis for Shimmer &
Savvy these days, but hey, I owe you, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev036601_MSG0051
rows.name:
Anyway, I'm willing to forget about profit and keep
buying back your miranium at ludicrous rates, okay?
So don't be be a stranger.[ST:wait ]
